Maybe it will be useful to someone. I add slug to model.ts:
interface ParentPlatforms {
  platform: {
    name: string,
    slug: string
  }
}
and add " index as i " to <img *ngFor>       

<img *ngFor="let gamePlatform of game.parent_platforms; index as i"
          class="game-platform"
          src="assets/images/platforms/{{ gamePlatform.platform.slug}}.svg"
          alt="{{ gamePlatform.platform.slug}}"
        />
